{
  "stem": "18665.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one-- one situation which is really closer to home, since I married my wife Marianne.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her father was thrown in jail by [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Goya. ?] He owned-- my father-in-law-- owned several pieces of property, and the Japanese wanted to buy it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but his partners were-- was a Russian and an Indian, a Sikh Indian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the decision was not only my father-in-law's to sell the property.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they tried to force him to sell the property by throwing him in jail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But apparently-- and he was there several weeks-- and my mother-in-law-- well, Marianne's mother, I never knew the lady-- had a heart condition.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that worsened her condition, and she eventually died in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very sad situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Turner at the time, but this is what my wife told me happened to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The property was outside of the district.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And exactly, I don't know, whether it was in the district or outside of the district.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That I don't know, because he owned several.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the conditions in jail were supposed to have been horrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very good with the Chinese.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That some of the Chinese learned to speak German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a friendly atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only ones who were not very friendly were the Chinese who collaborated with the Japanese on the Wang Jingwei who was the puppet regime.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Chinese were put in uniforms similar to those that Japanese wore, so they were the ones who showed their muscle.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the general population were happy that we were there, because they made a living from a lot of the immigrants.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had five refugee camps, different schools and where people lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- it became a very strong Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I believe even two.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
